reviewText: Film quality varies from good to awful, transfers are cropped too tightly. Please don't believe the front or back of the box. There are many short black and white excerpts from peep machine loops. There is no color. None of the segments have titles. The toplessness is nearly continuous, as the undressing was removed with the titles. There is occasional complete nudity. Even so, I almost regret purchasing this item. The bargain price pretty much excuses the faults, though. Its hard to complain seriously about an hour or so of okay vintage nudes for less than the price of a bad fast food lunch.
